lead_paragraph: Frank Lampard scored his second goal of the match three minutes into stoppage time to give New York City FC a 3-2 victory over D.C. United on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Frank Lampard Scores Twice, NYCFC Beats DC United 3-2
